Class ImageTransferStats

java.lang.Object
  com.kallasoft.smugmug.api.json.entity.ImageTransferStats

public class ImageTransferStats

Class used to define an image and all the transfer statistics that can be reported for it.

Constructor Detail

ImageTransferStats

public ImageTransferStats(org.json.JSONObject imageObject)
                   throws IllegalArgumentException
Construct a new image transfer stat object by safely parsing all known image values out of the given JSONObject.

If a property is not available from the JSONObject, it's value is simply set to null and ignored and parsing continues.

Parameters:
imageObject - The JSONObject that will be queried for all the image transfer stats.
Throws:
IllegalArgumentException - if imageObject is null.
